"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n目前，只有美國、俄羅斯、中國大陸、法國和英國擁有射程超過5000公里的洲際導彈。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n原來日本咁落後架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本定期射火箭上太空<br />\n你覺得如果佢要整導彈整唔整到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何止上太空？<br />\n日本已經可以於探測器到磒石表面，掘完石再返地球<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你估支那狗咁，少少事就打晒飛機咩"},{"pid":"451a3e95fefbe9e7f5e2103260d5491a2de2b7eb","tid":55913,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n目前，只有美國、俄羅斯、中國大陸、法國和英國擁有射程超過5000公里的洲際導彈。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n原來日本咁落後架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本戰後禁止擁有主動攻擊武器</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本要整既話，開條生產線外售都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3377adec31055f355b7f9b7d52bcd5093c16d36a","tid":55913,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"其實日本依家射衞星支火箭有固體燃料版<br />\n即係要射就隨時射，唔駛等入燃料，同洲際彈導導彈一樣"},{"pid":"1730e07cdc5ca979b0b9c081c5199f511ade231f","tid":55913,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日凝住呢d野會禁錯掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你怕印度發射支核彈失敗仲好過諗佢按錯掣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n射射下又變左射煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咪on9 印度火箭發射連績成功率已經第二，追緊俄羅斯個世界紀錄<br />\n而且商業發射亞洲最多生意"},{"pid":"fd72494dd75d485c006f7bd45a55bdaa0143359e","tid":55913,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知，大陸打飛機只會打載人火箭計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但完全唔會提深空探測，<br />\n日本係世界第四個射人造衛星上太空、<br />\n世界第三個向月球射探測器、<br />\n同世界第一個令到探測器登陸完小行星又返到地球既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外日本仲有金星探測器射撚埋上太空，<br />\n中國撚有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfe89a638c78fd7390e84c5f60daabf7676cdda","tid":55913,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家知唔知，大陸打飛機只會打載人火箭計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但完全唔會提深空探測，<br />\n日本係世界第四個射人造衛星上太空、<br />\n世界第三個向月球射探測器、<br />\n同世界第一個令到探測器登陸完小行星又返到地球既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外日本仲有金星探測器射撚埋上太空，<br />\n中國撚有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，原來講印度，<br />\n當我順便屌埋隔離國家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02175c5e4280972c16d00066840e493580bb43b5","tid":55913,"uid":6439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"枝導彈係咪印度佬人手投擲出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}